<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for the 2007 Microsoft Office System (KB972581)</Title><Description>A security vulnerability exists in the 2007 Microsoft Office System that could allow arbitrary code to run when a maliciously modified file is opened. This update resolves the vulnerability so that the 2007 Microsoft Office System documents are handled appropriately.</Description><MoreInfoUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/kb/972581</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/?LN=en-us</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>